[NEW] REVOSA Natural Eyeliner

Author: @cmdr_nova@mkultra.monster

Published: 14 Oct 2015


New from REVOSA, the first product in our line of facial cosmetics, natural eyeliner!

Liner comes in 4 different version, all with a little bit of shadow. Colors are black, white, black & white and red.

You may have noticed that the face is different, and this is because I’ve decided to return to using a system body head. One, because I want to do a product line of different types of facial cosmetics and two, because the TMP head just isn’t allowing for the customization I’m used to (and in 2 and a half weeks, I haven’t heard back from their team about appliers/installers).

Marketplace: https://marketplace.secondlife.com/p/REVOSA-Natural-Eyeliner/7882406

Inworld: http://maps.secondlife.com/secondlife/Pisces/201/208/27
